com.collation.platform.model.topology.sys.zOS
Interface ZSeriesComputerSystem

All Superinterfaces:
CIMSystem, ComputerSystem, ConfigurationItem, LogicalElement, ManagedElement, ManagedSystemElement, ModelObject, java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
LPAR, ZVMGuest
public interface ZSeriesComputerSystem
extends ComputerSystem

A computer system that is built using zSeries architecture (and commonly runs operating systems such as zOS). The ZSeriesComputerSystem represents the instance of physical hardware, the box (CEC) that a z/OS image executes on

Persistable:
true
Top Level:
true
